snippet.title: Shoujo Kakumei Utena: Itsuka Kakumei Sareru Monogatari - Part 1/10 (Utena Ending)
snippet.description:
Shoujo Kakumei Utena: Itsuka Kakumei Sareru Monogatari (Also Revolutionary Girl Utena - The Tale of the Four Day Revolution) is a sega saturn game released in 1998 based in the series. 

Hi again! I'm planning to play this whole game (all their endings).
I'm playing this game on an emulator 'SegaSaturnF_012_beta_R3'. I tried to use an average resolution for a better record and view in general (remember is a quite old game)... so all excuses apart! Enjoy it and hoping it has a good reception (:

Want more Shoujo Kakumei Utena: Itsuka Kakumei Sareru Monogatari?
My playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLf1OIPK4El-J-C2iFTFlz6c9Xk6VdMP3_
